message.body: I guess they started a new chat... I thought it was for people around the world. Are you M or F ... I'm a 40 yr old F
I don't think it is location specific, its just text generating. I'm female, 32. What do you have planned for the weekend?
I'm up at my vacation place ..cleaning,decorating and spending money :) trying to get everything organized. Its like decorating a second home! Then a fire pit, drinks and rest!" How about you?
Did you just acquire this place? I'm heading to work in a moment, having a hard time leaving the park..
Congrats, that is exciting! Is it in the woods or on the water?

Woods!! Im more of a water/beach person but can only afford up in the woods but its nice and I didn't even know it but 2 of my employees live here about6 houses away so its great !!! What do you do for a living
Oh wow, what a coincidence. It always feels good to spend some time in the trees. I'm a student, studying at Bryn Mawr
I'm a retired Sgt. I worked in the jail... I prefer the ocean but my sons love the mountains
I'm split, I like both. How is retirement?
Its good!! A little boring at times but now that I have this place its giving me something to do
Will you be able to use it year round, or is it a seasonal home?
Yr round but I think I'll use it till it snows..too cold!!
Right, no point going north in the winter. Did you have a fire tonight?
Yes.... it was a nice night out. What's your plans for today? We're just hanging out around here..
